Cyberpunk style: A neon-drenched server room corridor where streams of glowing data packets flow like rivers between towering black monolithic server racks. In the center, a sleek chrome gateway structure acts as a funnel, redirecting the luminous data streams from multiple incoming paths into organized channels heading toward a single destination server pulsing with electric blue light. The scene is bathed in magenta and cyan hues, with holographic routing diagrams floating in the misty air. Rain streaks down distant windows, and cables hang like vines from the ceiling, their fiber optic cores glowing softly. The atmosphere is moody and technical, suggesting complex traffic management happening in real-time within this digital infrastructure.
